1
00:00:01,100 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,200
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:15,170
I'll take you to Hell!

5
00:00:15,170 --> 00:00:16,710
Go to Hell!

6
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:18,340
Prepare to rock!

7
00:00:18,340 --> 00:00:19,700
Juvia...

8
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:21,250
What's happened to you?

9
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:01,390
This is the ultimate vibe!

10
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:03,300
It's so loud!

11
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:06,180
Juvia... Is this because 
of the noise from that guitar?

12
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:09,200
Exactly!

13
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:15,400
Women who become my succubi 
can only hear my orders!

14
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:21,050
But if I captured both of you, 
the game would be booooring!

15
00:02:21,050 --> 00:02:25,500
What I wanna see is a good 
cat fight between two girls!

16
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:29,360
You know, one of those rip-roarin', 
jiggly, slippery, hair-pullin' affairs!

17
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,420
You're just the lowest.

18
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:32,210
Lowest?

19
00:02:32,210 --> 00:02:35,340
That's the <i>highest</i> praise you could give me!

20
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:39,970
It's time for little babies who don't 
understand rock to get spanked!

21
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:44,760
And I just changed clothes!

22
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,350
Now, then...

23
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:52,040
Which part should I devour first?

24
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:55,760
I think I should start with 
that dress! Too pretty for you!

25
00:02:59,380 --> 00:03:01,060
Heart's Armor!

26
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,790
This is it, yes!

27
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:13,810
What are you doing? Get a 
hold of yourself, Juvia!

28
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:28,890
Juvia! You want to join Fairy Tail, right?

29
00:03:28,890 --> 00:03:31,390
Attacking your allies isn't...

30
00:03:31,390 --> 00:03:35,110
Hey you! Heyah! Feel the vibe!

31
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:37,230
Get her!

32
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:40,150
Water Cane!

33
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:44,290
Yes, raise the roof with that red rhythm!

34
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:46,560
That's the soul of rock!

35
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,790
Says who?

36
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:50,470
I want more cat-fight with claws!

37
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:53,870
Do it like she's trying to 
steal away a guy you like!

38
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:55,570
Guy I like?!

39
00:03:55,570 --> 00:03:57,380
Love Rival!

40
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:59,230
I'm not!

41
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:03,300
It's no use...

42
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,320
She's completely under his control!

43
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,560
What should I do?

44
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:12,950
There's no way I could beat Juvia 
if she's fighting for real.

45
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:17,330
Die inside of Juvia!

46
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,680
I can't breathe...

47
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:23,120
Lucy-san... Lucy-san!

48
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,200
Juvia?

49
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:28,700
Lucy-san... Juvia isn't doing this.

50
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:30,630
Her heart is speaking to me?

51
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:33,160
Juvia doesn't want to hurt her friends.

52
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:37,050
Perhaps its presumptuous 
for me to say "friend..."

53
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:42,280
It's true that you are a rival in 
my love for Gray-sama, Lucy-san...

54
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,810
Although I'm not...

55
00:04:43,810 --> 00:04:48,440
But, Juvia has come to love Fairy Tail.

56
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:53,930
It's welcoming, and fun, and a warm place...

57
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:59,400
Even in the rain, it feels like 
the sun is out inside Fairy Tail.

58
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:05,910
Juvia had no idea it was okay to 
smile this much inside a guild!

59
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:11,740
That's what I thought... And just when I felt 
I could finally become friends with everyone...

60
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:16,750
Juvia truly is a woman 
that brings misfortune...

61
00:05:17,030 --> 00:05:21,880
Tears... Even inside the water, 
Juvia's tears are warm...

62
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,600
Juvia, baby!

63
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,840
It's about time to finish her off!

64
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:34,020
This will be the end for you!

65
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:39,400
People who shed tears for their friends...

66
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,560
...will never be rejected from Fairy Tail!

67
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:46,050
Lucy-san...

68
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,800
Go ahead and boast!

69
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:52,450
Thanks to you, I remembered 
something pretty neat!

70
00:05:52,450 --> 00:05:54,250
You're so boring.

71
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:58,350
Hurry up and destroy her, Juvia baby!

72
00:05:58,810 --> 00:06:00,080
Okay!

73
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,920
I'll tear you to shreds with my Water Jigsaw!

74
00:06:04,170 --> 00:06:06,300
Here's the big finish!

75
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:08,150
Lucy-san, dodge!

76
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:20,580
Gate of the Water Bearer, I open thee!

77
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,360
Aquarius!

78
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:25,860
What?!

79
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:28,570
She called a Spirit using Juvia's body?

80
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:32,990
As long as there's water, I can summon 
the most powerful Spirit, Aquarius!

81
00:06:32,990 --> 00:06:34,830
It's all thanks to you, Juvia!

82
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:38,160
Shut up, you!

83
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,240
You bratty little girls!

84
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:49,140
Don't you listen?

85
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:52,970
I told you that my hair can 
absorb water, remember?

86
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,110
Juvia!

87
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,850
I'm over here!

88
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:00,650
Juvia!

89
00:07:00,650 --> 00:07:02,650
Lucy!

90
00:07:09,470 --> 00:07:11,840
What... is this magical power?

91
00:07:12,810 --> 00:07:15,870
Those girls fused their magics together?

92
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,620
A Unison Raid!

93
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,900
What is this water?

94
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,880
This is more than I can absorb!

95
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,710
Sparking!

96
00:07:54,110 --> 00:07:55,420
We did it!

97
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:57,830
Juvia is back to normal!

98
00:07:57,830 --> 00:08:00,930
I'm glad... I'm so glad, Juvia.

99
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,730
Lucy-san, you're warm...

100
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:08,470
This might be the first time a 
woman has been nice to Juvia.

101
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:14,940
Hey, you! Don't go summoning 
me in freaky places!

102
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:18,840
You better not be plannin' on summoning 
me in a toilet bowl next, <i>right</i>?

103
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,810
I'll kill you, witch!

104
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:22,140
I'm sorry...

105
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,060
She's scary...

106
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:25,960
Don't get carried away.

107
00:08:26,450 --> 00:08:28,450
Right, I'm sorry.

108
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,800
I'll be going on a vacation with 
my boyfriend for two weeks.

109
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:36,330
Do <i>not</i> summon me, got it?

110
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:37,280
Got it.

111
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:40,050
Get a boyfriend yourself already.

112
00:08:40,050 --> 00:08:41,900
Hmph. As if that were possible.

113
00:08:41,650 --> 00:08:45,920
No boyfriend

114
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,600
Leave me alone!

115
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:45,920
Unrequited

116
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,920
Lucy-san, love is very important.

117
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,740
Anyway...

118
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:59,500
We managed to get one of them!

119
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,430
Things aren't going the way Jellal planned.

120
00:09:02,430 --> 00:09:06,100
No... It was you who defeated him, Lucy-san.

121
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:07,650
It was both of us.

122
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:13,880
You called me "Lucy" back then.

123
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:17,920
I was glad you did. It made 
us seem more like friends.

124
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:20,400
You don't have to add 
"-san" to my name anymore.

125
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:23,540
Since we're friends now, okay?

126
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,860
Huh?

127
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:34,850
Rain is falling from Juvia's eyes...

128
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:37,210
You have a funny way of saying things.

129
00:09:39,470 --> 00:09:42,970
Let's wait a little while 
we recover our strength.

130
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:46,060
Yes... Juvia will as well.

131
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:53,700
A Unison Raid?

132
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:58,900
The thing that monk spent his entire 
life studying in pursuit of?

133
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:02,120
I heard in the end he never attained it.

134
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:06,740
Even if it's coincidence, that's 
quite the nerve they have.

135
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:11,820
They may be little girls, but 
they are Erza's comrades, yes?

136
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:35,080
On the subject of attacking the 
Tower of Heaven with Etherion:

137
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:38,380
4 people for, 5 people against.

138
00:10:38,380 --> 00:10:43,350
As it stands we will resolve 
to hold off using Etherion.

139
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:44,450
Wait!

140
00:10:44,450 --> 00:10:47,540
Do you people really comprehend 
the situation we are in?

141
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:49,470
Don't make a scene, Sieg...

142
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:51,390
You've already had your say!

143
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:54,130
There are still peaceful 
ways of solving this.

144
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:56,000
Peaceful?

145
00:10:56,500 --> 00:11:00,210
While we're wasting time 
doing this pointless farce,

146
00:11:00,210 --> 00:11:03,780
Jellal is resurrecting the dead!

147
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:05,970
Can't you feel it?

148
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:08,150
The overflowing negative magical power...

149
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:11,400
That's the horror of who 
he is trying to resurrect!

150
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,530
What?

151
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:15,470
Siegrain, what exactly are you...

152
00:11:15,470 --> 00:11:20,700
I held back this information on the slight 
chance that it would leak out and cause panic.

153
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:22,450
But I have no choice...

154
00:11:23,090 --> 00:11:25,210
What are you talking about?

155
00:11:25,210 --> 00:11:26,700
Tell us everything!

156
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:28,240
The Black Wizard Zeref!

157
00:11:32,990 --> 00:11:34,990
Is that the truth?

158
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:36,250
Sieg!

159
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,080
It's the truth.

160
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:41,370
I understand Jellal better than anyone.

161
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:44,760
Because he's my twin brother, after all.

162
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,150
We will vote once again.

163
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:55,150
Hoo-hoot Kick!

164
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:59,660
Talons of the Fire Dragon!

165
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:07,300
You thought that would work?

166
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:11,300
He's a match for Natsu! That owl's good!

167
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:12,680
Of course.

168
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,870
He's one of Trinity Raven.

169
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:19,710
I'm about to to drop the iron 
hammer of justice upon you!

170
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:25,300
Missile Hoo-hoo-hoot!

171
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:29,470
And? Think that'd hit me?

172
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:31,810
Now, rise!

173
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:35,810
Arm hands!

174
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:43,280
Around the World!

175
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:46,360
His techniques are nonsensical, but fearsome.

176
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:51,110
No, way...

177
00:12:51,110 --> 00:12:54,580
I know your weakness, Salamander!

178
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:57,240
This is bad! That's transportation!

179
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:57,960
What?

180
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:00,420
Natsu can't handle transportation!

181
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:03,220
Going in for the kill when 
your opponent is weakened!

182
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:05,510
<i>That</i> is hunting!

183
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:12,810
Now! Capture Hoo-hoo-hoot!

184
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:18,680
What the hell are you doing?

185
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,650
Erza...

186
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,360
Do it again!

187
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:30,080
Why am I supposed to be super lucky today?

188
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,590
The result will be the same every time.

189
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:35,290
And wait, why wouldn't 
you be happy with that?

190
00:13:35,290 --> 00:13:37,080
Super lucky my butt!

191
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:40,500
This morning I got stuck in 
a ditch, lost my wallet...

192
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:42,420
Nothin' good has happened.

193
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:53,070
Who's the kid?

194
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:55,450
Here comes another weirdo, sheesh.

195
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:59,230
This is the place Grandpa Rob talked about.

196
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:07,670
What the...

197
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,810
Gray!

198
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:10,410
What's going on?

199
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:16,000
He's being eaten whole?

200
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:20,000
I digest the magical power 
of people I feed on!

201
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,500
Give back Natsu!

202
00:14:23,130 --> 00:14:26,050
Fire Hoo-hoo-hoot!

203
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,080
That's...

204
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,170
Happy!

205
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:35,610
He's digesting Salamander's magical 
power and taking it for himself?

206
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:36,970
How do you like that?!

207
00:14:37,810 --> 00:14:40,480
This is the skill of the Assassin's Guild!

208
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,310
The final blow!

209
00:14:46,450 --> 00:14:50,690
Sheesh... That's some crazy-hot fire there.

210
00:14:50,690 --> 00:14:51,850
Gray...

211
00:14:52,650 --> 00:14:54,800
A new challenger appears!

212
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,820
Hey, weren't you supposed 
to go after Sho and Erza?

213
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:59,800
He's held us up!

214
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:02,120
We need to find them quick 
or we're in trouble!

215
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:07,460
Jellal said that he was planning 
on using Erza as a human sacrifice.

216
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:12,300
I don't think there's anyone who 
can beat Erza when she's serious,

217
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:16,230
but she's too defenseless while 
she's trapped inside that card!

218
00:15:17,210 --> 00:15:20,350
It was a mistake to tell 
Sho everything all at once.

219
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:23,140
But I never thought he'd go crazy like that.

220
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:25,190
Gray...

221
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:28,690
Save Natsu!

222
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:33,470
I always gotta save your butt...

223
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:36,890
What are we supposed to do if 
you get yourself eaten, huh?

224
00:15:36,890 --> 00:15:38,830
You flaming piece of...

225
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:42,290
Digestion has begun!

226
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:46,950
In about 10 minutes Salamander's 
body with be dissolved!

227
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:51,940
And when that happens, his 
magical powers will be all mine!

228
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:57,970
I'll finish this up.

229
00:15:57,970 --> 00:16:00,020
Don't be so cocky!

230
00:16:01,020 --> 00:16:04,220
Ice Make Lance!

231
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:12,280
Roar of the Fire Dragon!

232
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:16,400
Dodge it! He has the same 
magic as Salamander!

233
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:22,910
You can't use ice within fire!

234
00:16:25,650 --> 00:16:26,670
Gray!

235
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:27,750
Not possible!

236
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:33,510
If you are Salamander's friend, than you 
should know how powerful these flames are!

237
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,520
She's always by herself, isn't she?

238
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,330
Why don't you go talk to her, Cana?

239
00:16:49,330 --> 00:16:52,400
She totally ignored me.

240
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:57,850
Well, I don't like it when a newcomer 
doesn't introduce herself to me, the great Gray!

241
00:16:57,850 --> 00:17:00,620
Since when did you start 
being such hot stuff?

242
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:04,250
Hey, you!

243
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:12,960
What are you doing?

244
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:15,240
This is a wizard's guild.

245
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:17,050
It ain't a place to be wearing armor!

246
00:17:17,050 --> 00:17:19,950
Then how about you wear 
something yourself, knave?

247
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:21,900
Is this a guild for perverts?

248
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:24,900
She sure told you!

249
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:26,890
Got to give her that one, Gray.

250
00:17:26,890 --> 00:17:29,400
Why, you...

251
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,860
Do not concern yourself with me.

252
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,870
The flames are freezing!

253
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:42,550
You call these Natsu's flames?

254
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,870
Don't make me laugh.

255
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:46,200
You're nothing but a damn poser!

256
00:17:47,430 --> 00:17:49,430
That's some impressive 
magical power you've got.

257
00:17:49,430 --> 00:17:52,190
I'll capture you as well!

258
00:17:53,670 --> 00:17:54,670
Gray!

259
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:57,590
Huh?

260
00:17:57,590 --> 00:18:01,090
Ack, that's cold!

261
00:18:01,090 --> 00:18:05,100
We don't have time to be wasting here!

262
00:18:05,100 --> 00:18:07,610
We have to catch up to Erza!

263
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:11,850
Did you get beat up by Erza again, Gray?

264
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:14,400
You don't give up, do you?

265
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,910
Could it be you're in love?

266
00:18:15,910 --> 00:18:16,990
Oh, shut up!

267
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:20,750
She's pretty amazing being 
able to get Gray like that.

268
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:24,950
Looks like the future of Fairy Tail will 
ride on the back of Erza the Great.

269
00:18:25,540 --> 00:18:28,540
I refuse to accept her as one of us!

270
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:31,500
I'm going to bring Erza back!

271
00:18:37,130 --> 00:18:40,000
I've found you, Erza.

272
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:43,050
Erza, it's on!

273
00:18:43,050 --> 00:18:45,810
Today, I'm finally going to beat you!

274
00:18:51,710 --> 00:18:52,940
It's you?

275
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:56,080
Sheesh, you never learn, do you?

276
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:59,640
Fine. Have at me.

277
00:19:01,020 --> 00:19:03,300
Uh... Well...

278
00:19:04,210 --> 00:19:06,700
What? You surrender already?

279
00:19:08,650 --> 00:19:12,580
Why are you always by yourself?

280
00:19:16,050 --> 00:19:18,090
I like being by myself.

281
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:21,220
I feel uncomfortable around other people.

282
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:22,910
Then...

283
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:26,640
Then why are you crying all by yourself?

284
00:19:39,840 --> 00:19:42,260
You won't have at me today?

285
00:19:42,260 --> 00:19:44,160
It's my choice!

286
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,120
Here I come!

287
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:55,790
Punch!

288
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,360
Outta my way!

289
00:20:02,590 --> 00:20:03,550
Ice Blade!

290
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:06,300
Seven Slice Dance!

291
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:18,560
He did it!

292
00:20:19,930 --> 00:20:21,410
She was always...

293
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:24,730
...by herself...

294
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:26,910
...her heart clad in armor...

295
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:29,870
...crying, all alone...

296
00:20:33,870 --> 00:20:35,700
Natsu!

297
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:37,720
W-Wow...

298
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:41,970
Erza must be in Fairy Tail!

299
00:20:41,970 --> 00:20:44,200
So she no longer sheds those tears!

300
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:48,720
8 people in agreement, 1 against.

301
00:20:49,570 --> 00:20:55,470
Therefore, Etherion is given permission 
to fire upon the Tower of Heaven.

302
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:00,560
We have a decision from the Council!

303
00:20:58,540 --> 00:21:01,110
Etherion will fire in one hour!

304
00:20:59,130 --> 00:21:01,890
Start the preparations! Hurry!

305
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:13,670
What is it?

306
00:21:15,330 --> 00:21:16,960
Pardon me.

307
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:18,950
Elder Yajima...

308
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:22,450
Sieg... Are you really sure about this?

309
00:21:22,980 --> 00:21:26,200
If you think about it carefully once again,

310
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:29,670
there might yet be another way.

311
00:21:30,050 --> 00:21:32,680
You may not agree with our methods,

312
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:36,100
but we cannot allow Zeref to be resurrected.

313
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:40,050
You know this, right, Elder Yajima?

314
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:46,300
I don't know anymore.

315
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:49,420
You will take full 
responsibility! Right, Sieg?

316
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:51,450
Of course. All responsibility lies with me.

317
00:21:51,450 --> 00:21:54,370
What I meant is that you will be 
responsible for the lives you will take!

318
00:21:55,880 --> 00:22:00,360
You are trying to send your 
own twin brother to oblivion!

319
00:22:00,360 --> 00:22:05,760
You will have to carry that loss of life on 
your back for the rest of your life, Sieg!

320
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:10,010
I will bear it.

321
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:12,520
I will bear the weight of Jellal's life.

322
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:18,980
So, what will you do? There's no time.

323
00:22:19,770 --> 00:22:22,650
Soon the light will rain down.

324
00:23:57,530 --> 00:23:59,210
Hey, what happened to the bird brain?

325
00:23:59,210 --> 00:24:02,530
Gray beat him while you were unconscious.

326
00:24:02,530 --> 00:24:05,650
What? Damn that underpants man!

327
00:24:05,650 --> 00:24:08,060
How dare he steal all the good parts!

328
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:10,100
Let's fight again!

329
00:24:10,100 --> 00:24:13,550
Natsu, we don't have time for that!

330
00:24:14,100 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: Destiny!

331
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:20,120
A-Anyway, beating Jellal 
would be way more impressive!

332
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:21,350
You think?

333
00:24:21,930 --> 00:24:23,450
Okay, let's go Happy!

334
00:24:23,450 --> 00:24:25,350
I'm worn out...

335
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:27,600


